title: Australia's Woodside sells 2 October Vincent crude cargoes at premiums - sources
text:
Australia's Woodside sells 2 October Vincent crude cargoes at premiums - sources

Commodities 41 minutes ago (Oct 03, 2019 18:11)

© Reuters. Australia's Woodside sells 2 October Vincent crude cargoes at premiums - sources SINGAPORE, Oct 3 (Reuters) - * Australia's Woodside Petroleum has sold two October-loading cargoes of Vincent crude at premiums above $6 a barrel to dated , two trade sources said on Thursday * The two 550,000-barrel cargoes were offered to load over Oct. 8-12 and Oct. 17-18 * The buyers were not immediately known * The spot premiums were much lower compared to other Australian heavy sweet crude grades - Van Gogh and Pyrenees - because Vincent just came back to the market after a long suspension and its quality needs to be tested, traders said
